DESCRIPTION:\nSunday\, March 15th | Maghreb to Fajr\n“A night better than a thousand months”.\nJoin us for the Night of Power – Laylat-ul-Qadr.\nThe night starts with a Community Iftar and ends at Fajr.\n7:12 pm | Iftar & Maghreb\n9:00 pm | Isha’a & Taraweeh\n12:00 am | Halaa with Imam Mohammed\n3:00 am | Tahajjud & Suhoor\n6:03 am | Fajr\n* We will complete Khatm-ul-Quran on Wednesday\, the 27th night.\nProphet (PBUH) said\, “Whoever prays on Laylatul Qadr out of faith and sincerity\, shall have all their past sins forgiven.” ~ Bukhari and Muslim\nThe rewards of giving in charity during Ramadan are multiplied by 70. The reward for any righteous act during Laylatul Qadr is equivalent to having performed the same act for over 83 years!\nDon’t miss the blessings of Layalt-ul-Qadr – Donate today.\nThe post Laylat-ul-Qadr appeared first on SALAM Islamic Center.\n\n\nMore info: https://salamcenter.org/events/laylat-ul-qadr-26/
DTEND:20260317T000000Z
LOCATION:SALAM Islamic Center
DTSTART:20260316T021000Z
SUMMARY:Laylat-ul-Qadr
UID:20260315191000-523a5222
