BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:\nThis is a memorization-based competition. Participants must:\nMemorize the assigned surah(s) for their level (by heart)\, and\nRecite with proper tajweed to the best of their ability.\nThis competition is open to all ages and skill levels\, with limited spots per category\, so please register early.\nImportant registration notes:\nRegister for one competition level only\nYou may move up an age group\, but not down\nCash prizes will be awarded to the top three winners in each category\nCompetition Categories\nLevel 1 (Ages 5-7): Surah Al-Ghashiya (Surah 888)\nLevel 2 (Ages 8-11): Surah At-Takwir (Surah 81)\nLevel 3 (Ages 12-15): Surah Al-Hashr (Surah 59)\nLevel 4 (Ages 16-18): Surah An-Najm (Surah 53)\nLevel 5 (Ages 19+): Surah Fussilat (Surah 41)\nHafiz Level: Surahs An-Nisaa’ & Al-Anaam (Surahs 4 & 6)\nThe post Quran Competition appeared first on SALAM Islamic Center.\n\n\nMore info: https://salamcenter.org/quran-26/
DTEND:20260308T010000Z
LOCATION:SALAM Islamic Center
DTSTART:20260307T203000Z
SUMMARY:Quran Competition
UID:20260307123000-1d992de7
END:VEVENT
